Script info: Prepares a Remote Runner user in Release

Input:
  #  password: Remote Runner password
  release:
    description: Digital.ai Release endpoint
    tag: digitalai.release.endpoint

---
Xl apply:
  endpoint: ${release}
  version: 23.1.0
  file: remote-runner-user.yaml

---
Http endpoint: ${release}

Http POST:
  path: /tokens/users
  body:
    tokenNote: cloud-connector-token

Output:
  token: ${output.token}
